<plot>Rehman is Deewan in a village, working for the Zamindar. His wife, Annapoorna promises his stepmother on her death-bed that she will take care of Rehman's stepbrother, Ramu. She fulfils her promise inspite of having her own son, Govind. They are one happy family till Annapoorna's widowed mother, Lalita Pawar comes to live with them. Tensions in the home mount as she tries to split the family between her daughter, son-in-law, grandson on one hand and Ramu on the other. Will she succeed in her efforts to split the family ? Will Annapoorna be able to choose between her love and duty for her own mother and her promise to Ramu's dying mother ?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?102228</url></doc>
